org.matsim.core.controler.listener

Interface ControlerListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventListener, MatsimExtensionPoint
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AfterMobsimListener, BeforeMobsimListener, DumpDataAtEnd, EventsHandling, IterationEndsListener, IterationStartsListener, PlansDumping, PlansReplanning, PlansScoring, ReplanningListener, ScoringListener, ShutdownListener, StartupListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExampleWithinDayController, ExecutedPlansServiceImpl, ModeStatsControlerListener, PtCountControlerListener, ScoreStatsControlerListener, WithinDayControlerListener

    public interface ControlerListener
extends EventListener, MatsimExtensionPoint
    ControlerListeners are notified at specific points in the Controler loop. See sub-interfaces for more information and specific usages.

    Example(s):

    • tutorial.programming.example07ControlerListener.RunControlerListenerExample
